tip.text: So goooood! They'll happily let you sample as many flavored as you want and when you're ready, a small is not small! I loved the blueberry and the chocolate cookie come was yummy!
Lobster rolls and steamers!!! I love this place so much! It's not mobbed with people and it's adorable. Sit outside on the picnic tables when you get your food and enjoy the beach views.
I tried 5 different lobster rolls on my Maine visit and this was by far the best lobster roll! They give you so much meat, it's super fresh, and the right balance of mayo/butter to lobster. Yum!!!
The wait was a bit too long for food that was just pretty good. Salad too sweet, lobster roll was ok, mussel curry was my favorite and fantastic. Salmon poke also a bit too sweet.
